version_description: this song is in the key of G#
This is the studio recorded version - it is apparent that the song is played with these chord shapes especially with the last strum of the song where you can hear the higher notes.
This is the full album version of this song played without a capo.

Complete version of the song making the difference between the open chords and the power chords giving the patterns. Moreover there are some unseful indications and the piano part is accurate. Please note that I made this tab on my own before seeing there was another which is according to me less accurate.
